Novak Djokovic has the right to be un-vaccinated ( for whatever reason )
 Australia has a Public Health policy . 
Proof of vaccination is required for entry from abroad. 
The decision is Djokovic's. 
Abide by Australia's rules or exercise his individual rights. 
The ball was in his court!
He chose.
